.nf
001\-Restart/s390vm14:
STOPPED  crm_verify\&.txt  hb_uuid\&.txt  openais\&.conf@   sysstats\&.txt
cib\&.txt  dlm_dump\&.txt    logd\&.cf@     permissions\&.txt
cib\&.xml  events\&.txt      messages     sysinfo\&.txt
.fi
.if n \{\
